{"text_id":192589,"tokens":["#"," How"," to"," Let"," Go"," of"," Someone"," Who"," You"," Deep","ly"," Loved","\n\n","##"," Understand"," the"," five"," stages"," of"," grief",".","\n\n","When"," you"," lose"," someone"," you"," deeply"," loved",","," whether"," through"," a"," breakup"," or"," other"," circumstances",","," it","'","s"," essential"," to"," recognize"," that"," you"," will"," go"," through"," a"," series"," of"," emotions"," known"," as"," the"," five"," stages"," of"," grief",":"," denial",","," anger",","," bargaining",","," depression",","," and"," acceptance","."," These"," stages"," are"," natural"," and"," help"," you"," process"," your"," loss","."," Knowing"," these"," stages"," can"," provide"," comfort"," and"," understanding"," as"," you"," navigate"," your"," emotions",".","\n\n","##"," Acknowledge"," your"," grief",".","\n\n","It","'","s"," vital"," to"," acknowledge"," and"," accept"," your"," feelings"," of"," grief"," instead"," of"," suppressing"," or"," ignoring"," them","."," Grie","ving"," is"," a"," part"," of"," the"," healing"," process",","," and"," acknowledging"," your"," pain"," is"," the"," first"," step"," toward"," recovery","."," Allow"," yourself"," to"," feel"," sadness",","," anger",","," and"," confusion"," without"," judgment",".","\n\n","##"," Share"," your"," grief"," with"," others",".","\n\n","Sharing"," your"," feelings"," with"," friends",","," family",","," or"," support"," groups"," can"," be"," cath","artic","."," It"," can"," be"," reassuring"," to"," know"," that"," others"," have"," gone"," through"," similar"," experiences"," and"," that"," you","'","re"," not"," alone"," in"," your"," suffering","."," Don","'","t"," hesitate"," to"," lean"," on"," those"," who"," care"," about"," you",".","\n\n","##"," Seek"," professional"," help"," if"," you"," need"," it",".","\n\n","Sometimes",","," letting"," go"," of"," someone"," you"," deeply"," loved"," can"," be"," overwhelming","."," If"," you"," find"," i